The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | Doc thrashed
                                                                                                               Doc thrashed
                            
	Suri, April 2: A surgeon has been hospitalised with head injuries and internal bleeding in his eyes after being hit by the relatives of a woman who died after an operation to remove kidney stones in a Rampurhat nursing home .        
	Dipak Chowdhurys vision in the left eye has been affected, said a doctor.         
	His house, near the nursing home 270km from Calcutta, was also attacked.                                                                                                                                                                              
